      <title>叙利亚叛军选出新总统并废除宪法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/syrian-rebels-name-new-president-and-dissolve-constitution</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据官方媒体报道，上个月推翻巴沙尔·阿萨德政权的叙利亚反政府武装解散了议会，拆除了国家武装机构，并任命了事实上的领导人为新总统，这一系列举措旨在为政治过渡铺平道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/syrian-rebels-name-new-president-and-dissolve-constitution</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 21:54:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称美联储在银行监管方面做得“很糟糕”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/trump-says-fed-has-done-terrible-job-on-banking-regulation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普严厉批评美联储的银行监管方式，并指责美联储主席杰伊·鲍威尔在抗击通胀方面失误，同时避免直接对利率发表评论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/trump-says-fed-has-done-terrible-job-on-banking-regulation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 21:45:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
