      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2025-01-28/could-trump-s-tariffs-slow-us-growth-it-happened-last-time</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储最新发布的记录显示，政策制定者在 2019 年竭尽全力保持经济增长。]]></description>
